or :

@PART[\*]:HAS[@MODULE[LaunchClamp]]  

{  

    @MODULE[ModuleGenerator]  

    {  

        @OUTPUT\_RESOURCE[LqdHydrogen]  

        {  

            @rate = 100 //1 is normal  

        }  

    }  

}

when that not worked, then the direct way into the cfg:

MODULE  

    {  

        name = ModuleGenerator  

        isAlwaysActive = true  

        isGroundFixture = true  

        OUTPUT\_RESOURCE  

        {  

            name = LqdHydrogen  

            rate = 20  

        }  

    }

